rows.label: tlk43600142_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Do you know what I want more than
anything else right now?

rows.label: tlk43600142_03_msg0003
rows.name: Or rather, I should say, security.

rows.label: tlk43600142_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I think that the way things are going,
Alst as we know it will be coming
to an end.

rows.label: tlk43600142_03_msg0005
rows.name:
The Divine Beasts have all gathered together
in one place and everyone's started
fighting each other. It's patently clear.

rows.label: tlk43600142_03_msg0006
rows.name:
There's no guarantee any of us will
make it out of this alive.

rows.label: tlk43600142_03_msg0007
rows.name:
But if anyone's out there willing to
help me survive, then, by God,
I'll pay them every penny I've got!
